public static class Nd4jCuda.FloatLogicOp
extends Nd4jCuda.FloatDeclarableOp
    Logic ops are unique snowflakes in any Graph. They dramatically change Graph Execution process, by introducing loops, conditions, etc. Their code is the part of GraphExecutioner logic. But we still want them to be expressed via Graph \tparam T
